{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"Progressive Web-Apps","mdn_url":"/de/docs/Web/Progressive_web_apps","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p class=\"summary\">Progressive Webanwendungen sind einfach Webseiten wie eh und je, nur besser.<strong> In einem modernen Webbrowser zeigen sie ihre Superkräft und werden </strong>…</p>\n\n<div class=\"column-container\" id=\"sect1\">\n<div class=\"column-1\" id=\"sect2\"></div>\n\n<div class=\"column-3\" style=\"height: 160px;\" id=\"sect3\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://mdn.mozillademos.org/files/12654/discoverable.svg\" style=\"float: right;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n<p style=\"font-size: 110%;\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Progressive_web_apps\"><strong>Auffindbar</strong></a></p>\n\n<p style=\"width: 70%;\">Als Anwendung erkennbar, mit Suchmaschinen auffindbar.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"column-3\" style=\"height: 160px;\" id=\"sect4\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://mdn.mozillademos.org/files/12656/installable.svg\" style=\"float: right;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n<p style=\"font-size: 110%;\"><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Progressive_web_apps\">Installierbar</a></strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"width: 70%;\">Auf Geräten verfügbar, auf dem Homescreen - ohne die Hürden von App Stores.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"column-3\" style=\"height: 160px;\" id=\"sect5\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://mdn.mozillademos.org/files/12658/linkable.svg\" style=\"float: right;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n<p style=\"font-size: 110%;\"><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Progressive_web_apps\">Verlinkbar</a></strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"width: 70%;\">Einfach per URL zu teilen, ohne schwierige Installation.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"column-1\" id=\"sect6\"></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"column-container\" id=\"sect7\">\n<div class=\"column-1\" id=\"sect8\"></div>\n\n<div class=\"column-3\" style=\"height: 160px;\" id=\"sect9\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://mdn.mozillademos.org/files/12660/network-independent.svg\" style=\"float: right;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n<p style=\"font-size: 110%;\"><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Progressive_web_apps\">Netzwerk unabhängig</a></strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"width: 70%;\">Funktioniert offline und bei schlechtem Empfang.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"column-3\" style=\"height: 160px;\" id=\"sect10\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://mdn.mozillademos.org/files/12662/progressive.svg\" style=\"float: right;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n<p style=\"font-size: 110%;\"><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Progressive_web_apps\">Progressiv</a></strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"width: 70%;\">Funktioniert für jeden, egal mit welchem Webbrowser.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"column-3\" style=\"height: 160px;\" id=\"sect11\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://mdn.mozillademos.org/files/12666/re-engageable.svg\" style=\"float: right;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n<p style=\"font-size: 110%;\"><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Progressive_web_apps\">Nutzer bindend</a></strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"width: 70%;\">Macht Nutzerbindung durch Benachrichtigungen einfach, auch wenn der Nutzer gerade nicht hinschaut.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"column-1\" id=\"sect12\"></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"column-container\" id=\"sect13\">\n<div class=\"column-1\" id=\"sect14\"></div>\n\n<div class=\"column-3\" style=\"height: 160px;\" id=\"sect15\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://mdn.mozillademos.org/files/12650/responsive.svg\" style=\"float: right;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n<p style=\"font-size: 110%;\"><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Progressive_web_apps/Responsive/responsive_design_building_blocks\">Responsiv</a></strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"width: 70%;\">Passt auf jeden Bildschirm: Desktop, Handy, Tablet oder was&nbsp; kommen wird.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"column-3\" style=\"height: 160px;\" id=\"sect16\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://mdn.mozillademos.org/files/12664/safe.svg\" style=\"float: right;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n<p style=\"font-size: 110%;\"><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Progressive_web_apps\">Sicher</a></strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"width: 70%;\">Sichere Verbindungen verhindern Datendiebstahl und garantieren Integrität.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"column-1\" id=\"sect17\"></div>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"https://developers.google.com/web/progressive-web-apps\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Progressive Web-Apps</a> bei Google Developers</li>\n <li class=\"graf--h3 graf--first\" id=\"4c45\"><a href=\"https://medium.com/@slightlylate/progressive-apps-escaping-tabs-without-losing-our-soul-3b93a8561955#.6czgj0myh\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Progressive Web Apps: Escaping Tabs Without Losing Our Soul</a> von Alex Russell</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"Progressive Webanwendungen sind einfach Webseiten wie eh und je, nur besser. In einem modernen Webbrowser zeigen sie ihre Superkräft und werden …","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Progressive web apps (PWAs)","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Aplicaciones Web Progresivas","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Applications web progressives","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"プログレッシブウェブアプリ (PWA)","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"프로그레시브 웹 앱","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Progressive web apps (PWAs)","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"Progressive web apps","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Прогрессивные веб-приложения","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"渐进式 Web 应用（PWA）","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"漸進式網絡應用程式","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/progressive_web_apps","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/progressive_web_apps/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/t